{"tid":2323555,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"玩完Cyberpunk2077後有感而發","createTime":"2020-12-13T09:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T04:16:10.000Z","uid":296364,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa2f6e5659fe78198353207408ec26ecd6188ca","tid":2323555,"uid":296364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"我自己一直都好鐘意Cyberpunk既世界觀，Mega corp, mega building, 身體改造等等由以前既人對未來既設想。Night city既setting乃至整隻game既世界觀都唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n我開始諗我地依家所身處既世界其實根本就係100年前嘅人所設想嘅世界，由可以喺天上飛既鋼鐵龐然巨物到高聳入雲嘅建築。呢啲嘢對以前嘅人來講只係一個幻想，而以前嘅人可以設想到呢啲嘢，我哋今時今日又諗到啲乜嘢？AI統治人類，機械人，身體改造，意識上傳？呢啲嘢我地幾十年前已經有。<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家所身處嘅社會係咪已經發展到冇嘢可以再俾我哋去幻想？定係純粹我哋越嚟越滿足呢個世界？又或者係我地嘅幻想力越嚟越差？"},{"pid":"3565f6152694e2af7516f44bc0ab1c43586e853c","tid":2323555,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef224bb4b811e1ee6e2c14c6b9b52f6192d5fa55","tid":2323555,"uid":38646,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"屌你打機就打機啦<br />\n懶感性"},{"pid":"0913b1adbfd8c9c6b5bf377175b56400ea9bf7f1","tid":2323555,"uid":335664,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ef224bb4b811e1ee6e2c14c6b9b52f6192d5fa55","tid":2323555,"uid":38646,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"屌你打機就打機啦<br />\n懶感性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"條友中二病發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4810d1746576585b3a4181ea45fda0fd4d3b9c","tid":2323555,"uid":119778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"兒登d廿零歲學生哥中二病又發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0123daeec82f9b94f52eada5ea9a0f479c9cd005","tid":2323555,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ad4df3